  "description": "Designed for dense, complex audio sources — crowd noise, dense ensemble recordings, full mixes. Low selectivity captures the full-spectrum energy mass. Low reactivity smooths over micro-variations, while maximum memory tracks the global energy arc across bars rather than individual events. Use when you want a coupled engine to ride the overall intensity envelope of a complete scene.",
